@startuml
!theme plain
skinparam defaultFontName Times New Roman
skinparam defaultFontSize 11

title Timeline SDLC Waterfall (4 Bulan)

scale 1.5

[Requirements Analysis] as REQ
[System Design] as DESIGN
[ML Model Development] as ML
[Backend Implementation] as BACKEND
[Frontend Implementation] as FRONTEND
[Integration] as INTEGRATE
[Testing & Evaluation] as TEST
[Deployment] as DEPLOY
[Documentation] as DOC

REQ is colored in LightBlue
DESIGN is colored in Lavender
ML is colored in LightGreen
BACKEND is colored in LightGreen
FRONTEND is colored in LightGreen
INTEGRATE is colored in LightGreen
TEST is colored in LightYellow
DEPLOY is colored in LightPink
DOC is colored in LightCyan

REQ lasts 14 days
DESIGN lasts 14 days
ML lasts 21 days
BACKEND lasts 14 days
FRONTEND lasts 14 days
INTEGRATE lasts 7 days
TEST lasts 14 days
DEPLOY lasts 7 days
DOC lasts 120 days

REQ -> DESIGN
DESIGN -> ML
DESIGN -> BACKEND
DESIGN -> FRONTEND
ML -> INTEGRATE
BACKEND -> INTEGRATE
FRONTEND -> INTEGRATE
INTEGRATE -> TEST
TEST -> DEPLOY
REQ -> DOC
DESIGN -> DOC
ML -> DOC
BACKEND -> DOC
FRONTEND -> DOC
TEST -> DOC
DEPLOY -> DOC

@enduml
